Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.06,0:00:17.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,希望是一种强大的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hope is a powerful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.10,0:00:20.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,梅兰妮用它来团结人民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Melanie used it to unite the people,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.69,0:00:21.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,先是用一个谎言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}first with a lie,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:25.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后承诺在雪国列车上的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but then with the promise of a life off of Snowpiercer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:31.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,安德烈·莱顿用希望来激励他的人民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Andre Layton used hope to inspire his people,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.24,0:00:32.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,争取自由\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to fight for their freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.41,0:00:35.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,但看看他的下场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but look where that's got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.37,0:00:41.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,而威尔福德先生就不一样了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And Mr. Wilford is a different story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.67,0:00:44.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,他把希望变为恐惧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's turned hope into fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.00,0:00:48.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,他让列车叛变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's turned the train against itself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.76,0:00:50.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后提出保护\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and then offered security.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.80,0:00:55.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,有趣的是  在他接管以后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The funny thing is, since he took control,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.39,0:00:58.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,一切似乎运行得都很顺利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}everything appears to be running smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.23,0:01:09.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,人人都参与工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Everyone is showing up for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.24,0:01:12.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,补给线井然有序\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The supply lines are a picture of order.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.54,0:01:18.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我们已经体验过了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But we've been here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.62,0:01:22.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,把那些递过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, hand those over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.17,0:01:25.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,快  快点  快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on, let's move. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.92,0:01:29.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,我自己的希望被我藏着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My own hope I keep hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:30.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,该走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.38,0:01:34.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,藏在为数不多几个能重新将其点燃的人手里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hidden in the few people who can rekindle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.31,0:01:39.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,我没有关于罗切和他家人的消息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've got nothing more on Roche or his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.97,0:01:41.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,装上货就快走  快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, load up and move! Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.48,0:01:45.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,威尔福德找我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wilford sent for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.86,0:01:47.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,你最好进来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You better come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.98,0:01:50.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.99,0:01:52.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,有我们在后车朋友的消息吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Any message from our friends downtrain?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.40,0:01:54.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们的信息都是一样的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They have the same info,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.86,0:01:56.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,安德烈在大爱丽丝化粪室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that Andre's in Big Alice Compost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:01:58.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们称其为沼泽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They call it the Swamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:01.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,知道威尔福德找我干什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Any idea what Wilford wants from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.25,0:02:03.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我尽量去打听  -好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I'll try and find out. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.92,0:02:06.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,他让我忙着策划一个特别之夜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's got me up to my eyeballs planning a special evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.21,0:02:10.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,好朋友奥德丽多半跟他说了我们的情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good friend Audrey probably told them all about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:12.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,不敢相信她信了他的花言巧语\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can't believe she fell for his shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:15.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,至少她知道她不该露面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}At least she's got the sense not to show her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:20.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,听着  要想在威尔福德先生的统治下幸存\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look, the way to survive Mr. Wilford,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.02,0:02:23.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,你就得对他有作用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you just gotta be something that he needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:25.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,你保持斗志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You keep your chin up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.48,0:02:27.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,遵命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.32,0:02:30.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,威尔福德先生的秩序\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Wilford's order
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.32,0:02:33.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,代价很高\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}comes at a very high price.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.95,0:02:36.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道有坏事将要发生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I just know that something awful is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.16,0:02:42.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,在雪国列车上  1034节车厢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}On Snowpiercer, 1,034 cars long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:03:00.59,特效,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\a6\c&H020202&\fs36\fn方正兰亭准黑_GBK\fsp8\t(\fsp11)\pos(192,85)}雪国列{\fsp0}车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:03:00.59,特效,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\a6\c&H020202&\fs24\fn方正兰亭准黑_GBK\fsp8\t(\fsp11)\pos(192,166)}{\fsp3\t(\fsp4.125)}第二季 第九{\fsp0}集\N{\fsp3\t(\fsp4.125)}"继续上演{\fsp0}"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.56,0:03:03.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,今晚的活动准备得怎么样了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How are the evening's festivities coming on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:05.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,在计划时间内  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right on schedule, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:07.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,我能问下  有宾客名单吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Might I ask-- is there a guest list?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.69,0:03:09.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,有的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:13.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,随机赢家  那是凯文的领域\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Random winners, that's Kevin's domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:17.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,他负责今天的一个特别惊喜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's in charge of a special surprise today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:20.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么样的惊喜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, what kind of surprise?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.87,0:03:22.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,给整辆列车准备的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}One for the whole train
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:25.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,庆祝合法的领袖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to celebrate rightful leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:26.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,你休息下吧  露丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Take some time off, Ruth,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:28.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,这样你也能好好享受下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so you can enjoy some of it too,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.13,0:03:32.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,但首先我要给你俩安排一项任务\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but first I have a job for the both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:34.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,我俩一起吗  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Both of us, sir, together?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.51,0:03:37.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,雪国列车变模糊了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Snowpiercer's getting muddy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:39.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,所有阶级都混在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}all the classes mixed up and down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:40.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,真是一团乱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:42.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们要开始一次完整的人口普查\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, you ought to begin a full census.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:44.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想要乘客像过去那样有组织\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I want the passengers organized like in the old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:48.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想知道谁在哪  在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I want to know who is where doing what.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:50.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,-遵命  -遵命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yes, sir. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:53.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,他会改变一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He'll change everything around now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.61,0:03:56.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,威尔福德想要适应力  我讨厌这词\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wilford wants resiliency. I hate that word.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.36,0:03:58.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,他想要我们分开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He wants to keep us apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:01.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,记住  他们会监听\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Remember, they're gonna be monitoring
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:03.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们在火车头之间的所有交流\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}everything we say between the Engines.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:06.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你会没事的  -到什么时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You're gonna be okay. - Yeah, until when?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:08.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,万一他把我关进沼泽呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What if he throws me in the Swamp?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:10.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,他在一个接一个地除掉我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's picking us off one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:13.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,他不能再失去工程师了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He can't afford to lose another Engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.34,0:04:17.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,-跟总部报告  -嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Check in with HQ? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:22.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你保持火车前进\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I need you to keep pushing this train forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:24.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们离接梅兰妮就剩一周了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're a week away from picking Melanie up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:26.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,-如果她在那的话  -她会在的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yeah, if she's there. - She'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.52,0:04:27.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经晚了一天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're already a day late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.02,0:04:29.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们在一周多前就失去了和她的联系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We lost contact with her over a week ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:32.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,但威尔福德不知道  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But Wilford doesn't know that, does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:34.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,保持这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, keep it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:39.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,安全让她回家  这就是任务  别问问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get her home safe. That's the mission. No questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:41.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,-好  -快点  该走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- All right. - Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.04,0:04:52.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,你也跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Y tú...vienes conmigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:04.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,惊喜是什么  凯文\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's the big surprise, Kevin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:07.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们越快开始普查  你就越早能知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The sooner we get the census going, the sooner you'll find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:08.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,拜托  我知道你迫不及待想要告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, come on, I know you're dying to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.89,0:05:10.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  发誓要保密\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sorry, sworn to secrecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:12.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你了解他的  -嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You know how he is. - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:17.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,这些是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What is all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.73,0:05:19.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,病人病历\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Patients' Records.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.03,0:05:21.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,从我的诊所里拿出来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Took 'em right out of my clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:24.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,这些不是乘客档案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}These are not passenger files.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:27.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,-这些是病历  -应该是保密的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- These are medical records. - Supposed to be confidential.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:28.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,他想要按年龄把他们分开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He wants them divided by age--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:31.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,小孩  青少年  18-39岁的  其余都算老人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}children, adolescents, 18 to 39. The rest, elderly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:33.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,老人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Elderly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:35.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.38,0:05:37.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,这些是为了什么  凯文\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's all this in aid of, Kevin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:39.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,我猜他想要看谁适合做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I guess he wants to see who's fit for what.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:42.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,每个乘客都要填写一份抽样调查问卷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A sample questionnaire for each of the passengers to fill out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:46.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是无票乘客吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Are you an un-ticketed passenger?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:49.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道跟反叛军一起作战过的任何乘客吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you aware of any passengers who fought with the rebels?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:51.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是为了存档  一个历史记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, it's for the archives-- a matter of historical record.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:54.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我会告诉他你不满意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll tell him you're displeased, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:56.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  凯文  你不能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, Kevin, you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:05:59.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会亲自和威尔福德先生谈话  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll have my own conversations with Mr. Wilford, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:04.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,我认识这车上的每个乘客\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know every passenger on this train,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:07.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,我认为我对他们每个人都负有责任\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I consider myself responsible for each of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.58,0:06:08.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,真扫兴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How unpleasant.
