Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:12.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,威尔福德让你做工程师  你就做好你的本职\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wilford tapped you as an Engineer. You're gonna stick to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:23.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:26.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,你妈从这回去的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}when your mom came back from here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:28.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,她说你不只是在技术方面很厉害\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}she said you weren't just technically good.
