Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:37.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,还好了  不如你妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mas o menos. Not like your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.92,0:07:39.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,让列车平稳行驶就是了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just keep us on the track.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:41.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,-好  你要去哪  -前车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Ok--where are you going? - Uptrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:45.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,今天是雪国列车的大日子  很遗憾你没被邀请\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a big day on Snowpiercer. I'm sorry you're not invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.43,0:07:56.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,我从大爱丽丝带来的  是我的最爱之一\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Brought her up from Big Alice, one of my favorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:07:59.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,你看到尸体纠缠在一起了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You see how the bodies are entwined?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.52,0:08:03.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,分辨不出他们究竟是在打架还是...  你懂的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can't tell whether they're fighting or... Well, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:05.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,你有什么想法  贝丝·提尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you think, Bess Till?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:07.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,我认为许多乘客都感到担忧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think a lot of the passengers are concerned.
