Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.41,0:08:13.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,莱顿  现在是司闸员罗切和他的家人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Layton and now Brakeman Roche and his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:18.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,你这人好打听\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're a curious creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:20.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道该拿你怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know what to do with you.
