Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.47,0:08:32.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,我从来都不需要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I never needed one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:33.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你知道为什么吗  -不  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You know why? - No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.97,0:08:36.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为以前我的列车上没有犯罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Because there wasn't any crime on my train.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:39.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在也没有犯罪  只有秩序\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There is no crime, only order.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.19,0:08:40.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,你应该没那么天真吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't think you're that naive.
