Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.40,0:08:50.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:52.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,你可以告诉乘客罗切先生进了抽屉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can tell the passengers Mr. Roche is in a Drawer
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:54.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,和他的家人一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}along with his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.58,0:08:58.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,等你们都安定下来  他们就可以回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When you all settle down, they can rejoin us.
