Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:10.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,赛克斯  带她到272车厢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sikes, take her down to car 272.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:13.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,不用担心莱顿先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And don't worry about Mr. Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.14,0:09:15.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们让他宾至如归\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We've made him quite at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.01,0:10:13.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在我知道你们只是在服从威尔福德的命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now I know you're just following Wilford's order,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:16.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我有权知道你们对我做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I have a right to know what you've done to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.35,0:10:18.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,你发现得太早了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You found out prematurely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.73,0:10:23.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错  我把手放进了冷锁处  却没被冻掉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, I put my hand in the cold lock, and it didn't fall off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:24.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,他对我到底有何目的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What does he want with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:25.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.28,0:10:29.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,你被送到我们这时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When you arrived with us--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:31.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,你没必要给我看这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You don't need to show me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.99,0:10:33.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,每一秒我都经历过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I lived through every second of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:35.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们把你修复好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We repaired you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:38.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:41.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们让痛苦消失了  但你们...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You took the pain away, but you...
