Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.06,0:11:41.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,快  我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.73,0:11:44.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,来  温妮  没事的  没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on, Winnie, it's all right. It's all right.
