Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:20.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,放出一个气球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and send a balloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:23.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有我们他们都疯了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They've gone mad without us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.35,0:14:27.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,-观察  -别去  妈妈  别去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Observe. - Don't go, Mama! Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.81,0:14:31.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,这不好笑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This isn't funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.82,0:14:42.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,别担心  你们在我的列车上很安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't worry. You're all safe on my train.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:45.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,永动机永不停息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Engine will provide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.67,0:14:57.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,我死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.17,0:15:00.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,威尔福德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:06.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,永动机永不停息  永动机永不停息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Engine will provide. The Engine will provide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:09.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,太精彩了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bravo, bravo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.69,0:15:18.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,确实精彩  你喜欢吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bravo indeed. Did you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:19.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,-喜欢  -很棒  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yeah. - It was good, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.49,0:15:25.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,别这样啊  你们都是怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, come on. What's wrong with you all?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:27.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,骗子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:31.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,真是可悲的尝试\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What a pathetic attempt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.33,0:15:35.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不能用这宣传方式杀死梅兰妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can't kill Melanie with this propaganda.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.38,0:15:38.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有多余的时间  已经晚了一天了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We don't have extra time. We're already a day late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:42.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,你似乎没留心看结尾  艾莉克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't think you paid close enough attention to the ending, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:44.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,我看了一眼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I got a peek at the launch data
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.05,0:15:46.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,你精心篡改的发射数据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that you so carefully doctored.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:50.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,本十天前就和梅兰妮失联了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ben lost contact with Melanie ten days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:01.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:07.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,在发射即将结束时  是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Towards the end of the launches, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:11.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们失联了  但梅兰妮能挺过难关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we lost contact, but Melanie is a survivor,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.41,0:16:13.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,她接收到的数据足够她建立气候模型\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and she received enough data to complete a climate model.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:17.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,好了  回火车头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, all right, back to the Engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:20.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,别放弃她  艾莉克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't give up on her, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:23.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,露丝  护送他们去前面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ruth, escort them forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.80,0:16:25.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,你还要为我的晚会做准备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You have my evening to prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:35.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,恕我直言  你可以把莱顿关起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}With respect, you can go ahead and lock up Layton,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.23,0:16:38.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,但你会发现在我们所有人身上都有他的斗志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but you'll find a bit of his fight in all of us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.78,0:16:51.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,今晚为少数人举办的私人活动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Private event this evening for a very select few.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:54.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:56.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,我可以把男朋友也带过去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Could I also bring my boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:16:58.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,他是清洁部主管\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's the head of Janitorial.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:16:59.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:02.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:07.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  凯文\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you, Kevin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.05,0:17:10.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,把你的建议放在打扮参加宴会上吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dress your next advice in evening wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.43,0:17:11.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,给\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:20.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,大家精神点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Everybody, look sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:23.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,威尔福德先生很快就会来到嘉年华\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Wilford will be through with the carnival soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.59,0:17:25.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后真正的表演就要开始了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and then the real show begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.18,0:17:27.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,这些是法国葡萄酒酒杯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Those are bordeaux glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:28.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在要喝的是加州葡萄酒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're serving zinfandel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.06,0:17:33.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,天呐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:35.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,跟着我说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now repeat it back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.02,0:17:37.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我们的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tell our friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:40.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,带个口信给乔茜  让她去化粪室找莱顿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get a message to Josie to find Layton in Compost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.11,0:17:42.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能放弃梅兰妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're not giving up on Melanie
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.61,0:17:44.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,或是离开这辆列车的梦想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or our dream of getting off this train.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:45.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能放弃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're not giving up--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:52.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,你想怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.66,0:17:54.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,狂欢节礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Compliments of the carnival.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:57.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,还有呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.71,0:17:59.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,晚餐邀请函\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}An invitation to dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:09.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,温妮  今晚等威尔福德忙的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Winnie, tonight when Wilford's busy,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.43,0:18:10.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,乔茜必须要找到莱顿好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Josie has to find Layton, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:12.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要他的帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We need his help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:03.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,调低一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Take it down slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:30.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,-稳定下来  -不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Level off. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:33.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,再降一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A little further.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:06.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,靠着墙站\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Against the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.69,0:21:04.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,在我梦里  你来找我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You come to me in my dreams, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:08.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,还挺吓人的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Rather spooky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.11,0:21:14.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以你还没把我的脑袋卡在舱门外面吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is that why you haven't stuck my head out a port yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:17.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,问个诚实的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Honest question.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:20.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,坚守你的理想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hanging on to your ideals,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:22.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,前车人们爱戴你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}being beloved by your people uptrain,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.21,0:21:26.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得这对最后的结果会有什么影响吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}do you think it makes the slightest difference in the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.96,0:21:27.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,有的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:30.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,对我而言  我看不到会有什么影响\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, for the life of me, I can't see how.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.98,0:21:34.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想我肯定是有什么特别的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I suppose there must be something uniquely wrong with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.93,0:21:37.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不特别  威尔福德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're not unique, Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.18,0:21:42.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,你就是个年长的白人列车独裁者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're an old, white dictator with a train set.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.73,0:21:46.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,就是像你这样脆弱又强大的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Fragile, powerful men like you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:49.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,当初把地球给冻住了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}froze the Earth in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.61,0:21:52.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  这是公关问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, it's a PR problem in that regard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.24,0:21:57.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,我没落下你的东西吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I haven't got any of your stuff left, have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.53,0:21:59.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,那种正直的麝香味\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That musky smell of integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.75,0:22:02.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,洗掉后  你的日子也就到头了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When that washes off, it's a wrap for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.71,0:22:05.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,你总是有你的跟随者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You'll always have your little followers,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.25,0:22:08.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,但大部分永远也不会如你希望的那样去爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but the majority will never love you like you want them to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.05,0:22:14.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,人民的意志  你是怎么忍受的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The will of the people-- how can you stand it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.34,0:22:17.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,每一个小分支\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Every little faction.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.26,0:22:20.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,政治权力的铁石心肠\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The cold heart of political power
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.89,0:22:23.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,就是服从\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is obedience.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.86,0:22:26.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,就是这些理念让我们总是成为敌人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That shit right there is why we'll always be enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.10,0:22:29.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉好多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.97,0:22:34.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要和你剩下的朋友在前车一起共进晚餐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm dining uptrain tonight with the last of your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.19,0:22:37.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,扎拉要做出一些决定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Zarah has some decisions to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.82,0:22:40.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,那你现在感受到爱了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So are you feeling loved now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.66,0:22:45.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,清理他们的粪便\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Up to your elbows in their shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.47,0:22:54.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,你敞开的心扉  莱顿先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your open heart, Mr. Layton,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.52,0:22:56.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,泄露了你的每一步\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it telegraphs your every move.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.59,0:23:10.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,天呐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My God.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.38,0:23:15.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,大家各就各位  幸运赢家来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Places, everybody. Lucky winners are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.06,0:23:16.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.70,0:23:20.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我的天  -不了  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Holy crap. - No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.34,0:23:22.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.43,0:23:25.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,我早该知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Should have bloody known.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.43,0:23:32.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么  露丝  最后的晚餐吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What are we in for, Ruth, the last supper?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.77,0:23:34.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,这一整天都是一场黑暗的展览\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This whole day's one long dark display.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.80,0:23:38.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,他和说这些邀请函给随机挑选出的客人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He told me the tickets were for random guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.39,0:23:39.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是凯文给我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Kevin dropped this on me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.02,0:23:41.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,把我关了一天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}after keeping me locked up
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:43.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,剥夺了我的所有舒适用品\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}all day for my comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.14,0:23:44.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果威尔福德威胁她的女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If Wilford threatens her baby,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.77,0:23:46.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,我就用黄油刀杀了他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm gonna kill him with my butter knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.41,0:23:48.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,好了  别激动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.48,0:23:51.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会尽可能地干预\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll run interference as best I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.79,0:23:56.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎各位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right, everybody, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.66,0:23:58.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,少数的幸运人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You lucky few.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.57,0:24:00.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,当列车里的其余人在参加狂欢节时\NWhile the rest of the train takes in the 当carnival,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.90,0:24:03.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,幸运赢家可以与威尔福德先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you winners get to enjoy a more intimate evening
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.79,0:24:04.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,共享一个更亲密的夜晚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}with Mr. Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.04,0:24:07.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.94,0:24:13.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,我浑身不自在  到底是要做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm a fish out of water, man. What's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.58,0:24:16.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,不知道  但就像你母亲常和你说的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know, but like your mother used to tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.27,0:24:20.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,-低调一点  -你们都吓到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- keep your head on a swivel. - You guys are freaking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.52,0:24:22.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,其实我超级兴奋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right, I'm actually super excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.65,0:24:26.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,那你呢  艾莉克斯  你也超级兴奋吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What about you, Alex? Are you "Super excited"?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.89,0:24:29.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想我们要完蛋了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think we're all screwed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:32.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,天呐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.99,0:24:40.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,当然了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Of course it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.41,0:24:42.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,大家好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hello, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.47,0:24:43.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,该死的奥德丽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bloody Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.48,0:24:47.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,我只想站在这里  看着你们所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just want to stand here and gaze upon you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.18,0:24:49.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,下来吧  约瑟夫  没必要大吼大叫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come down, Joseph. There's no need to bellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.74,0:24:52.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢一桌子的奇怪客人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I love an eccentric table of guests, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.83,0:24:55.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,新老朋友坐在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mix it up with old friends and new.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.70,0:25:01.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,纵情享受几道吃一次少一次的美味佳肴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Indulge our palates with a few dwindling delicacies.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.92,0:25:03.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,那不是邀请函吗  露丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Isn't that the ticket, Ruth?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.75,0:25:05.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,邀请函是你在负责  先生  和以往一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're in charge of tickets, sir, as it ever was.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.97,0:25:07.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,-威利  -在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Willy. - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.07,0:25:09.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,你能给我弹一曲钢琴吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Would you tickle the ivories for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.36,0:25:12.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,来吧  何乐而不为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Go on then. Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.86,0:25:15.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,她戴的是王冠吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is she wearing a freaking tiara?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.25,0:25:17.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,不要脸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shameless.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.50,0:25:25.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,*阳光午后*\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}*On a sunny afternoon*
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.60,0:25:29.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,*携手爱人*\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}*With one you love*
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.34,0:25:32.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,*星空高挂*\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}*The stars above*
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.91,0:25:36.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,*等待夜幕*\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}*Waiting for the moon*
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.77,0:25:42.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,*奏响风琴*\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}*The old accordion playing*
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.95,0:25:46.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,*多愁善感*\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}*A sentimental
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.00,0:25:46.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,-*歌曲*  -*小曲*\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- *Song* - *Tune*
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.76,0:25:48.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,是小曲  不是一首歌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a tune, not a song!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.81,0:25:49.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,凯文\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Kevin.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.65,0:25:53.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,*漫步河边*\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}*Cruising down the river
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.03,0:25:57.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,你有你的狂欢节  这里是我的地盘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You've had your carnival. This is my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.79,0:26:00.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,请去休息室待着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please stay in the lounge.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.51,0:26:04.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  他就交给你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Fine, he's all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.02,0:26:09.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,*漫步河边*\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}*Down the river
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.71,0:26:15.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,*阳光午后*\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}*On a sunny afternoon
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.33,0:26:24.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,真是太美好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, isn't this lovely?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.65,0:26:29.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,我应该撤走这些餐具吗  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shall I clear this setting, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.08,0:26:30.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  露丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.70,0:26:32.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,还有一个宾客\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's one last guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.29,0:26:35.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,小莱拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lilah Junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.56,0:26:38.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,当然  我认识你父母\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Of course, I knew your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.63,0:26:41.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,你我是第一次见  奥斯维勒先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're new to me, Mr. Osweiller.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.39,0:26:44.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩应该互相认识\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I believe you two know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.26,0:26:46.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,以前是司闸员搭档\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ex-Brakeman partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.79,0:26:48.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,-没错  先生  -嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- That's correct, sir. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.80,0:26:49.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,真有意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.61,0:26:54.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,不过艾莉克斯  你应该没见过扎拉吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, but Alex, I don't think you've met Zarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.02,0:26:58.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,-她是乘客服务部的  -也是安德烈·莱顿的伴侣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- She's with Hospitality. - Also Andre Layton's partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.07,0:27:01.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,-很高兴认识你  艾莉克斯  -幸会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- It's nice to meet you, Alex. - Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.63,0:27:04.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,前妻  对吗  奥德丽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ex-wife, wasn't it, Audrey?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.89,0:27:07.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,车尾离婚  也算数吧  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a Tail divorce. It sort of counts, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.24,0:27:11.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,在夜车里待了那么多年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All those years in the Nightcar...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.12,0:27:14.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们告诉你的那些私事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}all those personal things that we told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.78,0:27:18.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,那是她的使命  帮我们敞开心扉和哀悼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was her calling, helping us open up and grieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.27,0:27:20.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  好让她可以像妓女一样出卖我们的秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, so she could sell our secrets like a whore.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.79,0:27:23.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,好了  好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, now, now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.24,0:27:25.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,莱顿先生怎么说的  我们是一辆列车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What did Mr. Layton say? We're all one train together.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.90,0:27:27.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.06,0:27:28.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想着吃顿晚餐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I thought dinner would be a nice way
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.75,0:27:30.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,能让我们再次团聚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to bring us all together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.28,0:27:33.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,在上帝和奥德丽的指引下  列车一心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}One train under God and Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.21,0:27:37.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,她不喜欢那个木偶秀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She didn't like the puppet show.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.33,0:27:41.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,是吗  我觉得很好笑啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Really? 'Cause I thought it was hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.25,0:27:42.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,-真的吗  -嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Did you? Yeah? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.95,0:27:44.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,梅兰妮没有这里的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, Melanie's not as pure as everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.58,0:27:46.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,-想象中那么纯洁  -小莱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- around here thinks she is. - LJ.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.06,0:27:47.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得威尔福德先生今晚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think Mr. Wilford's heard enough
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.12,0:27:48.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,已经听了够多关于梅兰妮的事了  小莱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}about Melanie for one night, LJ.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.78,0:27:49.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,我没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.70,0:27:54.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想再听听关于我妈妈的谎言  莱拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I would love to hear more lies about my mother, Lilah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.85,0:28:01.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,她是骗子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, she was the liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.77,0:28:03.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,她想成为你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She wanted to be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.18,0:28:06.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,她指控我犯罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She accused me of a crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.46,0:28:08.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后我发现了她的小秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I found out her little secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.70,0:28:10.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以她不得不推翻判决结果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so she had to overturn the verdict.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.66,0:28:19.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,我困惑了  小莱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm puzzled, LJ.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.00,0:28:23.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果梅兰妮推翻了判决结果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If Melanie overturned the verdict,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.32,0:28:26.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,是不是就是说你确实有罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}does that mean you were guilty?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.92,0:28:32.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.74,0:28:37.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}no, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.50,0:28:41.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以你没有像我在文献里读到的那样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So you did not cut off those men's penises
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.43,0:28:43.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,割掉那些男人的阴茎吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}like I read about in the transcript?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.60,0:28:46.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,我真是松了口气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I am so relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.86,0:28:48.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是真的吗  莱拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is that true, Lilah?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.87,0:28:50.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,小莱是个好人  威尔福德先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lilah Junior is a good person, Mr. Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.10,0:28:53.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,-是的  -她父母去世后她的生活跌入谷底\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Oh, yes. - She fell a long way from First when her parents passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.28,0:28:54.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,她学会了工作  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She learned to work, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.28,0:28:57.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,她现在对列车很了解  我为她骄傲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She knows the train now, and I'm proud of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.22,0:28:58.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,他会说话啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He speaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.06,0:29:02.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,来自东密德兰的奥斯维勒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Osweiller from the East Midlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.47,0:29:05.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,你比你搭档还安静\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're even quieter than your partner,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.20,0:29:06.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,可靠提尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Trusty Till,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.25,0:29:10.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,不过更浪漫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}though a little more romantic, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.42,0:29:14.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,我对小莱的感情是真诚的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My intentions with Lilah Junior are sound, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.29,0:29:16.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,真感人  你听到了吗  奥德丽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How lovely. Did you hear that, Audrey?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.39,0:29:17.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,听到了  他是真心的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, and he meant it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.80,0:29:23.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我  奥斯维勒先生  我之前的卫生主管  特伦斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tell me, Mr. Osweiller, my previous head of Janitorial, Terence,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.87,0:29:26.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,他当初在我纽约的房子里任职\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I brought from my buildings in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.41,0:29:29.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么接替他位置的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How did you come to be in his shoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.19,0:29:31.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,先生  之前是段混乱时期\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sir, those were chaotic times.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.57,0:29:33.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们失去了很多人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We lost a lot of people in the troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.37,0:29:35.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们尽最大努力填补空缺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We've tried to fill in as best we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.22,0:29:39.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,这问题很简单  一个擅离职守的司闸员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A simple question for an AWOL Brakeman
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.24,0:29:42.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,以及一个用叉子挖掉她父亲眼睛的女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and a girl who put out her father's eye with a fork.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.20,0:29:46.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,仔细考虑下  奥斯维勒先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Think very carefully about this, Mr. Osweiller.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.85,0:29:49.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,我为什么要留着你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why should I keep you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.75,0:29:54.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,回到我  孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Answer me, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.38,0:29:59.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,我能去弹奏一曲吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.81,0:30:01.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,小奥  你在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Os, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.82,0:30:06.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,-他会弹吗  -不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Does he play? - I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.04,0:30:08.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,有段时间没弹过了  请见谅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's been a while, if you'll forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.54,0:30:11.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,大冰封后就没弹过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not since the freeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.84,0:30:31.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,*这是我写给你的冬季情歌*\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}*This is my winter song to you *
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.80,0:30:34.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,*风暴即将来袭*\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}* The storm is coming soon *
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.07,0:30:37.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,*它已在海面翻滚*\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}* It rolls in from the sea *
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.55,0:30:43.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,*我的声音如夜晚中的烽火*\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}* My voice a beacon in the night *
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.44,0:30:47.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,*我的话语会成为你的光亮*\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}* My words will be your light *
