Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.78,0:32:04.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,乔茜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.04,0:32:11.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,乔茜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Josie?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.01,0:32:16.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,稍等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}One minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.12,0:32:20.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.63,0:32:23.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,乔茜  让我看看你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Josie, let me see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.72,0:32:29.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,你好多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're better.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.51,0:32:31.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,别妄下定论\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, jury's still out on that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.98,0:32:33.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,他治好了你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He fixed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.70,0:32:36.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们时间不多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We haven't got much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.01,0:32:38.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,扎拉通过车尾联系了我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Zarah contacted me through The Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.81,0:32:40.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,她说他们还没放弃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She said that they haven't given up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.17,0:32:43.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们想知道下一步是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They want to know what the next move is.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.19,0:32:49.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,莱顿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.10,0:32:51.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,记住我们在为什么抗争\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Remember what we're fighting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.88,0:32:56.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,列车上的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Life off train.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.32,0:33:00.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,我可以尝试救你出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I could try and get you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.53,0:33:05.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你帮不了我  -别这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You can't help me. - Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.47,0:33:09.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们上次这样相见  我们发动了一场革命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The last time we met like this, we started a revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.67,0:33:11.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,他为你准备了计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He has plans for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.95,0:33:13.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,你得待在原地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You have to stay where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.96,0:33:20.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  我必须这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know. I--I need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.39,0:33:23.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道我怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know what's happening to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.97,0:33:27.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,感觉像是重生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It feels like-it's like being reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.64,0:33:32.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,还有希望  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There is still hope, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.85,0:33:36.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,你会找到你的时刻  我也会的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You'll find your moment. So will I.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.97,0:33:39.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,保持对他人的信心  我们仍在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Keep faith in the others. We're still together.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.63,0:33:40.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,时间到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Time's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.48,0:33:44.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,-够了  -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- That's enough. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.92,0:33:47.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他们我们会完成我们开启的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tell them we'll finish what we started.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.13,0:34:03.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,你有对手了  奥德丽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You have competition, Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.73,0:34:07.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  挺好的  很不错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}yeah, no, it was good. It's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.77,0:34:08.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,非常棒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bravo.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.11,0:34:12.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,还有人想唱歌吗  扎拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Anyone else wanna sing? Zarah?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.19,0:34:15.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,不了  我不再会为了我的晚餐而唱歌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, thanks. I'm done singing for my supper.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.17,0:34:17.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,她会唱的  她是个幸存者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}she'll sing. She's a survivor.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.84,0:34:19.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,来吧  露丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Join us, Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.67,0:34:22.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,我有些事要告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I have something to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.35,0:34:25.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,小心点  露丝  他的话一个字都别信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Be careful, Ruth. Don't trust anything he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.29,0:34:25.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.59,0:34:28.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,你认识我妈妈  而他在试图\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You knew my mom. Well, he's trying
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.14,0:34:30.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,让全车人反对回去接我妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to turn the train against going back for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.82,0:34:32.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,看在上帝的份上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}for pity's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.49,0:34:34.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,我为木偶戏的事感到抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sorry about the bloody puppets.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.59,0:34:36.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,她在轨道旁等着我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She's waiting trackside, and we have
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.33,0:34:38.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我们必须要完成任务  -不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- to complete this mission! - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.61,0:34:40.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,我已经不准备冒险带着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm no longer prepared
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.57,0:34:42.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们的两列火车再穿过那个山口了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to risk us taking two trains across that pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.94,0:34:45.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,你弄清楚人口普查是为什么了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you figured out what the census is for yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.23,0:34:46.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,你快弄清楚了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you close?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.94,0:34:49.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,是为了什么  威尔福德先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What is it for? Mr. Wilford?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.21,0:34:51.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不告诉他们你在大爱丽丝上都做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why don't you tell them what you did on Big Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.86,0:34:54.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,-够了  -我们一开始有两百人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- That's enough! - There were 200 of us at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.79,0:34:58.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是之后  当他发现我们要使用掉太多的资源时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but then when he realized what a drain of resources we were,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.92,0:35:00.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,他就剔除了一半的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we were, he culled half of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.53,0:35:02.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,男人  女人  小孩  他杀了他们所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Men, women, children, he took their lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.67,0:35:03.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么敢这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How dare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.97,0:35:06.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们的灵魂在上  你怎么敢这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}On their souls, how dare you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.11,0:35:07.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,逼我再经历那件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}make me relive it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.14,0:35:11.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,-带她去禁闭室  -别担心  我在禁闭室待过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Take her to the brig. - Don't worry. I've been there before.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.21,0:35:14.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,露丝  他要来对付你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ruth, he's coming for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.13,0:35:25.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,坐下  露丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sit down, Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.63,0:35:28.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的  先生  乘客服务部永远不可以坐下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}As you know, sir, Hospitality never sits.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.92,0:35:30.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,瞎说  你整晚都在疑惑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nonsense, you've been wondering
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.78,0:35:33.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,是谁要坐在那个位置\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}who that setting's for all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.15,0:35:36.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,-是为你准备的  -我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- It's for you. - Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.14,0:35:40.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  今天都是为你准备的  露丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, today's all about you, Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.78,0:35:42.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,坐下吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.45,0:35:46.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,凯文\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Kevin.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.07,0:35:48.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你在上面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know you're up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.46,0:35:50.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,下来吧  你这个淘气的小男孩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come down, you naughty, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.73,0:35:57.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,希望大家都玩得很开心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hope we're all having a wonderful time.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.91,0:36:02.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,露丝  我想感谢你准备了这么无懈可击的晚宴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ruth, I want to thank you for an impeccable evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.52,0:36:04.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,你超越了你自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You've outdone yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.51,0:36:09.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,凯文  我的小伙子  你经历了太多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Kevin, my lad, you've come through so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.39,0:36:11.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,你也成功的举办了一场惊艳的嘉年华\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and you've put on an amazing carnival.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.46,0:36:14.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,-是我的荣幸  先生  -坐下吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- It's my honor, sir. - Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.92,0:36:21.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道现在乘客服务部人员供过于求\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You understand there is a glut in Hospitality,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.62,0:36:26.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,意味着  部门主管只能有一个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}which means there's only room for one head of department.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.24,0:36:35.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个位置是你的  露丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Job's yours, Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.38,0:36:39.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I--oh--
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.73,0:36:40.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴  凯文\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shut up, Kevin.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.60,0:36:46.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,站在我身边吧  就像你以前一直想要的那样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}By my side just like you always wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.50,0:36:48.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,你要做的就是向全列车广播\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All you have to do is address the train,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.07,0:36:50.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,正式通知他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}inform them officially
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.45,0:36:52.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们不会回去接梅兰妮了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we're not returning for Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.82,0:37:12.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不能这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.46,0:37:14.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Beg your pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.01,0:37:22.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不会那么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I won't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.90,0:37:32.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是在拒绝我的邀请吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you rejecting my offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.11,0:37:44.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.56,0:37:48.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,把你的制服脱下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Take off your Teals.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.86,0:39:02.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,我承认  我在分辨道德上有障碍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I confess, I'm morally dyslexic.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.37,0:39:05.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,有的时候我分不清对错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sometimes I don't know right from wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.34,0:39:10.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,我花了些时间  但还是找到了适合你的位置\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It took a while, but we found you a role.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.38,0:39:12.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的顾问\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.46,0:39:14.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不确定我配得上这个职位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not sure I'm the person for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.98,0:39:16.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,瞎说  你完美契合\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nonsense, you're perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.49,0:39:17.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,你为自己考虑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You think for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.04,0:39:21.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,你经常在重大的道德问题上挣扎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You struggle with the big moral questions--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.42,0:39:22.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,自由  正义\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}freedom, justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.71,0:39:24.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,你可以告诉我  我哪里错了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can show me where I'm going wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.62,0:39:27.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,-告诉我底线在哪  -你说的是什么底线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- show me the line. - And which line is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.94,0:39:34.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,你先请\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}After you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.85,0:39:43.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,这些是杀了维修队的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your Breachmen's killers.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.06,0:39:49.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想给你  你之前要求的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wanted to give you what you asked for,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.90,0:39:52.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,一个结案的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a chance to close the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.74,0:39:57.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们非常愿意执行我的命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They were only too happy to carry out my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.98,0:40:02.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,你只要说那个词  只要拉一下杠杆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just say the word, and one pull of the lever
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.91,0:40:05.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,就可以通过冰肺来执行正义\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}will deliver justice by lung of ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.45,0:40:10.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,这不是正义  正义需要公平的审判\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This isn't justice. Justice requires a fair trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.27,0:40:12.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.12,0:40:15.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,不仅仅是下个裁决吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not just a verdict?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.79,0:40:17.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们是按你的命令行事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They were acting on your behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.35,0:40:23.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,人人都是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, everyone does.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.88,0:40:27.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,这只不过是  把他们都收拾掉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This just...tidies it all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.11,0:40:28.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sir
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.99,0:40:36.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,我建议你不要这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I advise you not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.61,0:40:44.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果这是你的劝谏的话  那么好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, if that's your council, then fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.78,0:40:46.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,你可以走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You may go.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.57,0:40:50.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不认为你会喜欢看最后这一小部分的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't think you're gonna want to watch the last bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.11,0:41:22.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,靠墙站好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Against the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.72,0:41:37.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,这都是什么啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What fresh hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.76,0:42:32.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,他会告诉所有人她死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's gonna tell everyone that she's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.69,0:42:34.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,他知道我们和她失去了联系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He knows that we lost contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.98,0:42:35.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,他不会回去接她的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's not gonna go back for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.87,0:42:40.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,他只会把她丢在外面  让她自生自灭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's just gonna leave her out there on her own to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.20,0:42:42.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,而我们会死在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and we are gonna die in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.84,0:42:44.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,我从不认为你是个半途而废的人  露丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Never had you down as a quitter, Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.62,0:42:47.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,威尔福德有的只是恐惧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All Wilford's got is fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.72,0:42:49.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们有的比他多得多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We got so much more than that--
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.55,0:42:53.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们有支持我们的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}friends who got our back,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.32,0:42:55.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,那就是我们的力量所在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that is our strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.88,0:43:13.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,雪国列车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Snowpiercer.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.82,0:43:17.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,雪  雪国列车  听到请回答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Snow-- Snowpiercer, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.66,0:43:20.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,我现在应该在信号范围内了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I should be range now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.37,0:43:22.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,你收到了吗  我是梅兰妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you copy? It's Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.06,0:43:27.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是个优秀的工程师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're a fine Engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.88,0:43:30.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you...sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.01,0:43:31.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我压钱打赌  你要比本好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Better than Ben for my money.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.02,0:43:34.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是已经没有钱这个东西了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But there's no money anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.12,0:43:38.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在只剩下一件事要做了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's only one thing left to acquire.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.94,0:43:42.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们可以依靠的就是列车了  哈维尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All we can depend upon is the train now, Javier.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.69,0:43:44.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.12,0:43:48.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,先生  我可以用你的洗手间吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sir, may I use your restroom please?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.57,0:43:50.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.16,0:44:53.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.13,0:44:58.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.72,0:45:10.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}无线电联系成功  梅兰妮还活着  哈维尔
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.11,0:45:14.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,安德烈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Andre.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.52,0:45:17.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,是哈维写的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's from Javi.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.33,0:45:21.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,梅兰妮  她联系上我们了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Melanie, she made contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.07,0:45:28.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,你准备好开始聊聊怎么离开这里了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You ready to start talking about getting out of here?
